#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:2
msgid "Auxiliary Interfaces"
msgstr "辅助接口"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:5
msgid "Registering an Interface"
msgstr "注册接口"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:7
msgid ""
"Class interfaces can be registered if you want to guarantee that script "
"classes implement a specific set of class methods. Interfaces can be "
"easier to use when working with script classes from the application, but "
"they are not necessary as the application can easily enumerate available "
"methods and properties even without the interfaces."
msgstr ""
"如果您希望确保脚本类实现一组特定的类方法，可以注册类接口。"
"在应用程序中处理脚本类时，接口可能更易于使用，但它们并非必需，"
"因为即使没有接口，应用程序也可以轻松枚举可用的方法和属性。"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:20
msgid ""
"Unlike the raw AngelScript interface, you don't need to add the class "
"name into the declaration of member ``funcdef`` for asbind20."
msgstr ""
"与原始 AngelScript 接口不同，对于 asbind20，"
"您不需要将类名添加到成员 ``funcdef`` 的声明中。"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:24
msgid "Type Aliases"
msgstr "类型别名"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:26
msgid ""
"Function definitions can be registered when you wish to allow the script "
"to pass function pointers to the application, e.g. to implement callback "
"routines."
msgstr ""
"当您希望允许脚本将函数指针传递给应用程序时，可以注册函数定义，"
"例如实现回调例程。"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:29
msgid ""
"Enumeration types and ``typedef``\\ s can also be registered to improve "
"readability of the scripts."
msgstr ""
"枚举类型和 ``typedef``\\ s 也可以注册以提高脚本的可读性。"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "参数"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:36
msgid "Example code:"
msgstr "示例代码："

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:49
msgid "Enumerations"
msgstr "枚举"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:66
msgid ""
"Up until version 2.39, AngelScript used a 32-bit integer to store the "
"underlying value of enums, before it supported customizable underlying "
"types. Please make sure those values don't overflow or underflow."
msgstr ""
"在 2.39 版本之前，AngelScript 在支持可自定义底层类型之前，"
"使用 32 位整数来存储枚举的底层值。请确保这些值不会溢出或下溢。"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:70
msgid ""
"Besides, the library provides a convenient interface for generating "
"string representation of enum value at compile-time."
msgstr ""
"此外，该库提供了一个便捷的接口，"
"用于在编译时生成枚举值的字符串表示。"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:72
msgid "The following code is equivalent to the above one:"
msgstr "以下代码与上述代码等效："

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:81
msgid ""
"However, as static reflection is still waiting for C++26, this feature "
"relies on compiler extension and is platform dependent. **It has some "
"limitations**. For example, it cannot generate string representation for "
"enums with same value."
msgstr ""
"然而，由于静态反射仍在等待 C++26，此特性依赖于编译器扩展且与平台相关。"
"**它有一些限制**。例如，它无法为具有相同值的枚举生成字符串表示。"

