#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:95
msgid ""
"Since the version 2.39, AngelScript supports enumerations with custom "
"underlying types."
msgstr ""
"自 2.39 版本起，AngelScript 支持具有自定义底层类型的枚举。"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:97
msgid ""
"You can register them by ``enum_underlying``, which is an alias of "
"``enum_<Enum, std::underlying_type_t<Enum>>``."
msgstr ""
"您可以通过 ``enum_underlying`` 来注册它们，"
"它是 ``enum_<Enum, std::underlying_type_t<Enum>>`` 的别名。"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:116
msgid ""
"If you need to interact these enums from C++ side, the enums with custom "
"underlying type :ref:`need to specify the conversion rules <custom-rule-"
"for-enum-underlying>`."
msgstr ""
"如果您需要从 C++ 端与这些枚举进行交互，具有自定义底层类型的枚举 "
":ref:`需要指定转换规则 <custom-rule-for-enum-underlying>`。"

